      .row
        .col-md-6
          h2 About 
          p
            | Welcome to Your Travel Blog, a place where we share our passion for travel and exploration.
          p
            | Our goal is to inspire you to discover new destinations, embrace new cultures, and create unforgettable memories.
          p Join us on this journey and let's explore the world together!
        .col-md-6
          img.img-fluid.rounded(src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/cdn.designcrowd.com/blog/2018/May/5-Steps-to-Designing-an-Eye-Catching-Travel-Blog/DI_5-Steps-To-Designing-An-Eye-Catching-Travel-Blog_Banner_828x300.jpg' alt='About Image')
